wikipedia_page.main: Luke Holden (born 24 November 1988), also known as Luke Holden-Moakes, is an English footballer who plays as a midfielder.

response: *Rhyl, TNS and Charlton Athletic player Luke Holden had a two-game spell at Formby in February/March 2012. He re-signed for Formby at the start of 2012–13, had a further spell away before signing for a third time in the summer of 2013.
